# Advanced Source Configuration Examples

This file shows all optional advanced source configurations.

## AgentMail (Email Digest)

```env
EMAIL_DIGEST_ENABLED=1
AGENTMAIL_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
AGENTMAIL_INBOX_ID=inbox_xxxx
AGENTMAIL_API_BASE_URL=https://api.agentmail.to
AGENTMAIL_LIMIT=50
AGENTMAIL_ALLOWED_SENDER_DOMAINS=alphasignal.ai
EMAIL_DIGEST_PUBLISH=0
```

## X API

```env
X_API_ENABLED=1
X_BEARER_TOKEN=your_bearer_token_here
X_API_QUERY=(AI OR "artificial intelligence" OR "large language model" OR LLM) lang:en -is:retweet has:links
X_API_MAX_RESULTS=20
X_API_DAILY_POST_LIMIT=50
X_API_RUN_UTC_HOUR=14
X_API_RUN_UTC_MINUTE_MAX=30
```

## OPML/RSS

```env
# Base64 encode your private OPML file and set as secret:
FOLLOW_OPML_B64=W3sicm9vdCI6Li4ufV0=
RSS_MAX_FEEDS=10
```

## Cost Notes

- Core pipeline: FREE (uses public RSS/feeds only)
- X API: ~$0.005 per post read
- AgentMail: depends on your plan

All advanced sources are **disabled by default**. Enable only what you need.